5|$|Fig.9 shows a doppler {{image of}} the <b>solar</b> <b>corona</b> made using a tunable Fabry-Pérot {{interferometer}} to recover scans of the <b>solar</b> <b>corona</b> {{at a number of}} wavelengths near the FeXIV green line. The picture is a color-coded {{image of the}} doppler shift of the line, which may be associated with the coronal plasma velocity towards or away from the satellite camera.|$|E
